snippet.title: Luenell on Chaka Khan vs Ariana Grande, Lori Harvey, Dr. Dre, NBA YoungBoy, Mase (Full Interview)
snippet.description: In this VladTV exclusive, regular guest and occasional interviewer for the platform, Luenell stopped by to discuss a host of topics. She weighed in on the comment Chaka Khan made about Ariana Grande during their interview. Luenell discussed the potential toll the divorce is taking on Dr. Dre's health but questioned whether a lot of women felt any sympathy for him considering his past with domestic abuse. She also gave her take on NBA YoungBoy having several BM's and why she would encourage her daughter to emulate Lori Harvey.
